Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-AE Assign Reviewers occurrences across all cases
Metric: Number of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' activities

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers that are immediately followed by SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers that are followed by SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Frequency of SW-AE Assign Reviewers appearing in variants that eventually lead to SW-EIC Accept
Metric: Number of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Frequency of SW-AE Assign Reviewers appearing in variants that eventually lead to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: Number of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Reject' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers that occur after SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers that are repeated more than once within the same case
Metric: the average of the function base > 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Frequency of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in cases where SW-Reviewer No Response occurs
Metric: Number of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers that precede at least one SW-Reviewer Agreed in the same trace
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Ratio of SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed across the entire event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Percentage of variants containing SW-AE Assign Reviewers that also contain Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1 or Reviewer Invitation Reminder 2
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Frequency of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in traces that include Assign a Different Editor or Unassign Editor
Metric: Number of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' activities for cases where activity 'Assign a Different Editor' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers that occur before SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers that are not followed by any reviewer response (i.e., no SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, or SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all cases where 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' does not happen

Name: Ratio of SW-AE Assign Reviewers to total reviewer-related activities (including SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, SW-Reviewer Unavailable, SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Frequency of SW-AE Assign Reviewers occurring after a deadline-related activity (e.g., SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days, SW-Reviewer Selection is now due)
Metric: Number of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in traces that ultimately result in manuscript acceptance (ending with RW-EIC Accept or SW-EIC Accept)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Percentage of SW-AE Assign Reviewers that appear in the top 5 most frequent process variants
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in cases that undergo multiple rounds of revision (e.g., containing both SW–Major Revision due in... and RW–Major Revision due in...)
Metric: Number of 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' activities
